==Letter==
'''W''', '''w'''

#The 23rd letter of the [[Wiktionary:About Roman script|English alphabet]], preceded by [[V]] and followed by [[X]], and representing /w/.
#A symbol of the [[IPA]], representing a [[voiced]] [[labial]]-[[velar]] [[approximant]].
